data.description: Nestled in the coveted Pelican Harbor, this charming .23-acre lot radiates tranquility. Surrounded by lush, mature trees for privacy and community walkways, it offers a splendid view of sunrise over the lake. The home welcomes you with 100k of upgrades, fresh Sherwin Williams paint, new LVP flooring, and a cleverly designed split floor plan under vaulted ceilings. The kitchen boasts new Frigidaire Gallery appliances, custom cabinets, and elegant quartz counters. The spacious primary suite features high ceilings, a large closet, and updated amenities. Every detail, from light fixtures to plumbing valves and faucets, has been meticulously upgraded. Enjoy modern comforts with a 2023 Trane AC and a well-maintained 2017 roof. The screened lanai leads to a pool and spa, now heated with a new Hayward gas heater. The backyard is a haven with designer landscaping and a large powered shed, perfect for hobbies. This home is a treasure trove of upgrades, making it a standout property!
